<title>USA: Conseco closes $300 million securities offer.</title>
<headline>Conseco closes $300 million securities offer.</headline>
<dateline>CARMEL, Ind. 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Conseco Inc said Tuesday it completed its public offering of $300 million in 8.796 percent capital securities of Conseco Financing Trust III, a subsidiary trust of Conseco, at $1,000 per security.</p>
<p>Each security will pay cumulative cash distributions at the annual rate of 8.796 percent, payable semiannually beginning October 1, 1997.</p>
<p>Conseco said proceeds from the offering of about $296.7 million, after underwriting and other associated costs, will be used to repay bank debt.</p>
<p>((--Chicago newsdesk, 312-408-8787))</p>
